<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="now-n">now <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /naʊ/    美 /naʊ/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>现在；此刻：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That’s all <strong>for now</strong>. 
眼下就这些。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I suppose he has arrived in Beijing <strong>by now</strong>. 
我想他现在已经到北京了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Up to / until now</strong>, the program has saved thousands of children who would otherwise have died. 
到目前为止，这项计划已经挽救了成千上万原本没救的孩子的生命。</p><footer>2010 山东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>From now on</strong> I will try to do better. 
从现在起我要争取做得更好。</p></div></div>